articles.author: Joseph White
articles.title: Tesla wants to start building a new U.S. vehicle plant this summer
articles.description: Electric vehicle maker Tesla Inc wants to start building a large vehicle assembly plant in the southwestern United States as early as the third quarter of this year, the company told Texas officials in documents made public this week.
